## Scroll animation

Globe section is NOT pinned. On scroll-into-view:
- Globe canvas fades in + scales from 0.92→1.0 (GSAP, 0.9s ease-out)
- Headline clips up (same pattern as About)
- Arc paths animate in with `arcDashAnimateTime` staggered per arc

